                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span>Both roles seeded in <code>SeedData.cs</code></li>
                        </ul>

                        <p class="fw-semibold mb-2">1b – Account Manager (AM) Role</p>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-2">External users. Sign up normally, assigned AM role. Access strictly limited to CS Live Help only.</p>
                        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4">
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span><code>InternalOnly</code> policy registered in <code>Program.cs</code> — blocks AM from all internal controllers</li>
