                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span>Add AM to <code>[Authorize]</code> on <code>CsLiveHelpController</code> (AM-facing actions)</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span>Strict server-side input validation + rate-limiting on all AM POST actions</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span>Audit log (<code>AmAuditLog</code>) for every AM action</li>
