                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-secondary">Todo</span><strong>Smart action — Reset Password:</strong> "Send Reset" → auto-posts system comment <em>"Password reset to Aa123456"</em></li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-secondary">Todo</span><strong>Smart action — Escalated:</strong> "Mark Passed" → auto-posts system comment <em>"Passed to relevant agents"</em></li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-secondary">Todo</span><code>POST /CsLiveHelp/Escalate/{id}</code> — move card to Escalated column</li>
                        </ul>

                        <p class="fw-semibold mb-2">1d-iv – CS Team Leader / Manager View + Requests All Brands <span class="badge bg-success ms-1">Complete</span></p>
                        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4">
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span><code>GET /CsLiveHelp/RequestsAllBrands</code> — shared internal board for all CS roles (agents, TL, Manager)</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span>TL/Manager default view filtered to Escalated; agents see all open items across all brands</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span>CS agents can post new internal requests directly on this board</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span>All CS roles can post comments and update card status on this board</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span><code>POST /CsLiveHelp/ResolveEscalation/{id}</code> — TL/Manager marks escalated card resolved/completed</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span>Sidebar: "Team Board" for CS agents; "All Brands" under CS Support (TL/Manager)</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-danger">Deferred</span>Image/file attachments on boards <em>(details TBD)</em></li>
                        </ul>

                        <p class="fw-semibold mb-2">1d-v – UX / Polish <span class="badge bg-success ms-1">Complete</span></p>
                        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4">
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span><strong>Comment visibility</strong> — "View Thread" button/modal on every CS board card shows full comment thread with author, timestamp, body, and system-message badge</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span><strong>Drag-and-drop column transitions</strong> — SortableJS integration on all 5 columns; drop fires <code>POST /CsLiveHelp/UpdateStatusJson/{id}</code> via fetch with antiforgery token; DOM badge updated inline</li>
