                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span><strong>Real-time board updates</strong> — SignalR hub pushes <code>CardAdded</code>, <code>CardUpdated</code>, <code>CardDeleted</code>, <code>CardStatusChanged</code>, <code>CommentAdded</code>; board DOM updated live via <code>cslivehelp.js</code></li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span><strong>POI Simulation smart action — modal</strong> — "Log Simulation" button on CS board card opens POI log modal pre-populated with card's brand via <code>/PoiSimulation/LogPartialWithBrand?brandId={id}</code></li>
                        </ul>

                        <p class="fw-semibold mb-2">1d-vi – SignalR Hub <span class="badge bg-success ms-1">Complete</span></p>
                        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4">
