                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span>Events pushed from all 12 controller mutation actions: <code>CardAdded</code>, <code>CardUpdated</code>, <code>CardStatusChanged</code>, <code>CardDeleted</code>, <code>CommentAdded</code></li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span><code>wwwroot/js/cslivehelp.js</code>: connects to hub, handles all push events, updates board columns and comment thread modals live</li>
