                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span>Cursor/keyset pagination — <code>GetBoardRequestsAsync(afterId)</code> uses <code>Where(r =&gt; r.Id &gt; afterId).Take(50)</code></li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span>Created <code>CsRequestArchiveService</code> (<code>IHostedService</code>) — configurable via <code>CsLiveHelp:Archive</code> in <code>appsettings.json</code> (defaults: every 6 h, Completed &gt; 3 days old)</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-0"><span class="badge bg-success">Done</span>Board columns load top 50 cards; "Load more" button fetches next page via <code>GET /CsLiveHelp/BoardPage?status=X&amp;afterId=Y</code></li>
